| Principle  | Description                   | Design Tip                               |
| ---------- | ----------------------------- | ---------------------------------------- |
| Spacing    | Deliver lessons over time     | Weekly or bi-weekly cadence              |
| Emotion    | People recall what moves them | Add real-world impact stories            |
